relation: A collaboration design with Cap'n Muffin and chuggaaconroy for their EarthBound: Memoirs game. Art by me. Ideas partly mine, partly theirs.
I forget who all contributed to this iscribble work, but almost all the colouring was by me.
Ness and Paula watching the sun set against the waves of Summers' beach.
